snippet.textDisplay:
This is Hands down the Most Creative and Soul Feeding Compostition I've ever come across. Thank You Coke Studios. Thank you Strings. Thanks to every artist especially Abida Parveen and Amjad Sabri for time really stopped for me when I heard you. 
Be it Hindu or Muslim or India or Pakistan, This is clearly a testament to the saying, "Music is the language of love." This hit me right in the feels. Anything Patriotic is always heart touching. And Pakistan, you're lucky to have such composers and compositions. Love, Respect and Happiness from India. :)
